Package: shinylabel
Type: Package
Title: R-Native Image Annotation Tool for YOLO Object Detection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
person(given = "Lalit", family = "BC",
email = "[lalitiaas@gmail.com](mailto:lalitiaas@gmail.com)",
role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an interactive 'Shiny'-based interface for image annotation
with support for drawing bounding boxes, managing multi-annotator workflows,
and storing annotations in a 'SQLite' database. Includes utilities to export
annotations in 'YOLO' and 'COCO' formats. Designed as a fully R-native
alternative to tools such as 'LabelImg' for object detection workflows.
